data.description: Charming bungalow with the perfect balance of original features and modern updates. Custom brick stairs leads to the covered porch and the enclosed heated/cooled sun porch. This is the perfect spot for greeting guests or that morning coffee. Beautiful wood flooring throughout the other living spaces and bedrooms with tile in the kitchen and bath. The bright living room leads into the formal dining room with fireplace. Original built-ins in the dining room for your china and extra storage. Updated and large kitchen has tons of prep and storage spaces. Island with butcher block, farm house sink, gas range and all appliances included. Both bedrooms feature multiple windows, ceiling fans and ample closets. This home sits on a fenced corner lot. Off street parking on a double drive as well as a carport/garage with sliding doors is located behind the gate. Entertain on the multilevel deck under the canopy shade of the mature oak tree. Enjoy your oasis in the heart of the city. Contact us today for your private tour!
